onboarding_survey.messages.1.text: Thank you! To complete this programme, you won‚Äôt be alone. You‚Äôll have a parenting guide by your side. There are two supportive parenting experts you can choose from:

Dan is a 42 years old dad and a dedicated paediatrician. Over the years, he has seen how loving & supportive relationships help children thrive and stay healthy. That's why he teaches parents and talks on podcasts about building strong, caring connections with their kids.
